subject: Horse Racing
Breeders' Cup World Thoroughbred Championships
lead_paragraph: Street Sense pulled a big upset in the $2 million Breeders’ Cup Juvenile on Saturday, shooting through along the rail to win by 10 lengths at Churchill Downs.
